(.text+0xe55): undefined reference to `__moddi3'
/usr/lib/ocaml/3.09.2//libasmrun.a(ints.o): In function `caml_int64_div':
(.text+0xe9e): undefined reference to `__divdi3'

Does anyone has a solution ?

